&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;cite&gt;A Matter of Oaths&lt;/cite&gt;, by Helen S. Wright; copyright 1990;
ISBN 0-445-20983-6.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I saw this recommended on the Internet somewhere, in August or July
